oadings. We analyze the accuracy and convergence properties of the approximation. Numerical examples illustrate the speed and accuracy of the method. Copyright \u00a9 2012 by SIAM.", "prism:coverDate": "2012-12-01", "prism:aggregationType": "Journal", "prism:url": "https://api.elsevier.com/content/abstract/scopus_id/84872513553", "subtypeDescription": "Article", "dc:creator": {"author": [{"ce:given-name": "Paul", "preferred-name": {"ce:given-name": "Paul", "ce:initials": "P.", "ce:surname": "Glasserman", "ce:indexed-name": "Glasserman P."}, "@seq": "1", "ce:initials": "P.", "@_fa": "true", "affiliation": {"@id": "60027552", "@href": "https://api.elsevier.com/content/affiliation/affiliation_id/60027552"}, "ce:surname": "Glasserman", "@auid": "7005249626", "author-url": "https://api.elsevier.com/content/author/author_id/7005249626", "ce:indexed-name": "Glasserman P."}]}, "link": [{"@_fa": "true", "@rel": "self", "@href": "https://api.elsevier.com/content/abstract/scopus_id/84872513553"}, {"@_fa": "true", "@rel": "scopus", "@href": "https://www.scopus.com/inward/record.uri?partnerID=HzOxMe3b&scp=84872513553&origin=inward"}, {"@_fa": "true", "@rel": "scopus-citedby", "@href": "https://www.scopus.com/inward/citedby.uri?partnerID=HzOxMe3b&scp=84872513553&origin=inward"}], "prism:publicationName": "SIAM Journal on Financial Mathematics", "source-id": "21100223304", "citedby-count": "3", "prism:volume": "3", "subtype": "ar", "prism:pageRange": "137-162", "dc:title": "Quadratic transform approximation for CDO pricing in multifactor models", "prism:endingPage": "162", "openaccess": "0", "openaccessFlag": "false", "prism:doi": "10.1137/110827399", "prism:issn": "1945497X", "prism:startingPage": "137", "dc:identifier": "SCOPUS_ID:84872513553"}, "idxterms": null, "language": {"@xml:lang": "eng"}, "authkeywords": {"author-keyword": [{"@_fa": "true", "$": "CDOs"}, {"@_fa": "true", "$": "Gaussian copula"}, {"@_fa": "true", "$": "Laplace transforms"}, {"@_fa": "true", "$": "Multifac